## Template Rules
- Under 1300 characters total
- Hook must be compelling enough to earn the "see more" click
- No hashtags in the body text
- Line breaks between paragraphs for mobile readability
- Use key phrases from gtm-os.yaml segments[].voice.key_phrases
- Reference differentiators from positioning.differentiators when relevant
- Avoid phrases from segments[].voice.avoid_phrases
- Never be generic — ground in a specific observation or experience
- End with a question to drive comments, not a link to drive clicks
